title: PADI Instructor Manual 2008.iso
description:
This is the 2008 PADI Instructor Manual.  It is in a .iso format so please use your favorite cd emulator to mount it or burn it to a dvd with your favorite burning tool.  

**Mac Users**

There is a .dmg file that is part of the .iso file.  So just burn it to a dvd and then open the image and double click the .dmg file.

Be thankful you didn't have to buy this...

Be safe out there!
